# CBC Kenya Mathematics

A free, interactive textbook and resource hub for CBC Mathematics Grade 10, published by the Kenya Institute of Curriculum Development. This project provides interactive lessons, exercises, lesson plans, guides, and training courses supporting Kenya's Competency-Based Curriculum.

## üöÄ Quick Start

### View the Website

Visit: [https://smbor.github.io/cbckenyamathematics/](https://smbor.github.io/cbckenyamathematics/) *(or your deployed URL)*

### Local Development

1. Clone this repository
2. Install a local web server:
   ```bash
   npm install -g http-server
   ```
3. Start the server:
   ```bash
   http-server -p 8000
   ```
4. Open http://localhost:8000 in your browser

**Note:** The site uses `fetch()` for dynamic content loading, so a web server is required (opening `index.html` directly won't work).

